se a full death's worth of experience so we can do half the damage that a wizzie is doing with a regular spell.  And that's not even getting me started on critical damage, which we aren't qualified for (/shrug .. beats me).  As if EE spells weren't enough of a joke, with the focus item effects, they're falling even further behind the times.</P><P><BR> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
